name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: V & S brothers - Авто из США

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The application is created for everyone who wants to buy a car at auto auctions in USA.  The application tools help to calculate the delivery to the destination as well to identify the vehicle ownership documents. 

It also identifies the participant in the application as well as the bidder at auction and gives all the necessary information for trading!
